{"id":232662402,"title":"今日微失眠來寫詩","content":"https://i.imgur.com/hY2WXzl.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/L66WkEM.jpg\n暮色蒼茫大地\n那顆暖紅色的淡黃\n緩緩的在雲被之中\n輕柔地藏著身軀\n只留下了映照的餘暉\n\n醉翁拎著一壺佳釀\n坐在岸邊\n自顧自地沉浸\n舉杯邀明月 \n對影成三人\n此刻正是開懷縱飲之時啊\n更待何時呢\n醉翁喃喃自語\n滿意的笑著\n\n啊\n正所謂\n半夢半醒\n暮色蒼茫\n煞是醉人矣","excerpt":"暮色蒼茫大地，那顆暖紅色的淡黃，緩緩的在雲被之中，輕柔地藏著身軀，只留下了映照的餘暉，醉翁拎著一壺佳釀，坐在岸邊，自顧自地沉浸，舉杯邀明月，對影成三人，此刻正是開懷縱飲之時啊，更待何時呢，醉翁喃喃自語","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-10T15:56:28.482Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-10T15:56:28.482Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":1,"tags":[],"topics":["新詩","創作","隨筆","詩"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"竹林八閒","department":"cof58drink98fee","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/hY2WXzl.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/L66WkEM.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"e217d91c-66e4-4a88-86af-5095d9361d94","url":"https://i.imgur.com/hY2WXzll.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/hY2WXzll.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hY2WXzll.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-10T15:56:28.482Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-10T15:56:28.482Z"},{"id":"e217d91c-66e4-4a88-86af-5095d9361d94","url":"https://i.imgur.com/hY2WXzl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/hY2WXzl","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/hY2WXzll.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-10T15:56:28.482Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-10T15:56:28.482Z"},{"id":"14ceee9a-7361-4bbc-999f-75524efe597c","url":"https://i.imgur.com/L66WkEM.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/L66WkEM","thumbnail":"https://i.im